creator: St.Paul's Lutheran Church
descriptionHtml: This app will help you stay connected with the day-to-day life of St. Paul's Lutheran Church. With this app you can: watch or listen to past messages; stay up to date with push notifications; share your favorite messages via Twitter, Facebook, or email; and download messages for offline listening.
descriptionShort: Powerful content and resources to help you grow and stay connected.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New Media Search Experience with support for Speakers, Topics, and Scripture tags
- New Related media section on Media Items shows other media tagged with the same Topics
- Enhanced user profile with additional field and a direct integration to our CMS for Messaging Customers
- Misc. bug fixes and improvements.
